# Backend (FastAPI) - `apps/apis`

Laravel-style layout. Run: `pnpm dev:backend` â†’ `uvicorn main:app` on port 8000.
PostgreSQL via asyncpg; `db` service in `compose.yaml`. Alembic migrations run on API startup (DDL only).

## Folder layout

```
apps/apis/
  main.py                    # uvicorn entrypoint (imports bootstrap.app)
  bootstrap/                 # FastAPI factory + ASGI app
  config/                    # settings, security, exceptions, dependencies
  app/                       # application code (Laravel app/)
    models/                  # M - SQLAlchemy ORM
    http/
      controllers/           # C - handler classes (no route decorators)
      dtos/                  # request/response Pydantic DTOs
    helpers/                 # model â†’ DTO serialization (totals, nesting)
    repositories/            # data access - ALL SQL here
    services/                # business logic
  database/                  # connection, migrate.py, migrations/, seeders/
  alembic.ini                # Alembic config (one revision per table)
  routes/
    api.py                   # all routes â†’ app/http/controllers
  prompts/
```

Flow: **controller â†’ service â†’ repository â†’ model â†’ db**.

## Layer rules

- **Controllers** (`app/http/controllers/`) - handler classes; delegate to services.
- **Routes** (`routes/api.py`) - define paths and wire them to controller methods.
- **Services** (`app/services/`) - business logic; raise `AppError`s.
- **Repositories** (`app/repositories/`) - every query; subclass `BaseRepository[Model]`.
- **Models** (`app/models/`) - SQLAlchemy ORM only.
- **Schemas** (`app/http/dtos/`) - Pydantic request/response DTOs.
- **Helpers** (`app/helpers/`) - model â†’ response serialization (totals, nesting); `response.py` builds the `{ success, message, data }` envelope.
- **Database** (`database/`) - connection + seeders live **outside** `app/`, like Laravel.

## Rules

- All config from `.env` - no defaults in `Settings` (see `.env.example`)
- Default admin user in `database/seeders/user.py` only - not in env vars
- AI calls server-side only; validate AI JSON before use
- Prompt at `prompts/quotation-draft.md`
- n8n webhook on approve - graceful failure; approval still succeeds
- All API responses use `{ success, message, data }` via `app/helpers/response.py`; errors use the same shape with `success: false`

## Env & deps

- `pyproject.toml` packages: `app`, `bootstrap`, `config`, `database`, `routes`
- Install: `uv pip install -e ".[dev,lint]"` from `apps/apis/`
- Copy `.env.example` â†’ `.env` before running
- Migrations (DDL): `make migrate` / `make migrate:rollback` / `make migrate:reset` - runs in the `api` container (migrate also on API startup)
- Reset schema: `make migrate:reset` or `make migrate:reset seed=1` (schema + seed)
- Shorthand: `make migrate:reset-seed`
- Seed only: `make seed` - runs in the `api` container (idempotent; not run on startup)
